rows.label: qst700806_msg0002
rows.name:
I thought I'd never be found
here, but you found me, mo!?

rows.label: qst700805_msg0102
rows.name:
All right? You're going to go
apologize to the old woman properly.

rows.label: qst700805_msg0201
rows.name:
Hahaha! You're naive!
There's no place in this
capital that I don't know!

rows.label: qst700805_msg0202
rows.name:
Now, if you're done, I'll have you
go to that old woman's place!

rows.label: qst700805_msg0301
rows.name:
Haha, in this world, there's no
such thing as "absolutely."

rows.label: qst700805_msg0302
rows.name:
Now, you will go and apologize
to the old woman, won't you?

rows.label: qst700805_msg0401
rows.name:
Your thinking is naive. More importantly,
Oulu-san is waiting for you.

rows.label: qst700805_msg0501
rows.name: Fufufu, you were quite good at hiding.

rows.label: qst700805_msg0502
rows.name:
Now, you will go to that old
woman's place, won't you?

rows.label: qst700805_msg0601
rows.name:
You know... your short,
stout bodies... stand out
no matter where you are.

rows.label: qst700805_msg0602
rows.name:
Now, you're done, right? Hurry
up and go to that old granny.

rows.label: qst700805_msg0701
rows.name:
Hmph... Your training
is still insufficient.

rows.label: qst700805_msg0702
rows.name:
After you've apologized to that old
woman, you should continue to devote
yourself to further training.

rows.label: qst700805_msg0802
rows.name: Now, go quietly to that lady.

rows.label: qst700805_msg0901
rows.name:
The camouflage ability of the
Nopon is surprising, but...

rows.label: qst700805_msg0902
rows.name:
Let's end this game of
hide-and-seek and have you go
to that lady's place, shall we?
